        ],
        "subject": "Sent Emails",
        "body": "1. Project Update\n   - To: david.smith@bluesparrowtech.com\n   - Cc: julie.williams@bluesparrowtech.com\n   - Body: 'Hi David,\n   \n   Could you please send me the latest update on the Phoenix Project? Julie might also need to review the documents.\n   \n   Thanks,\n   Emma'\n\n2. Client Meeting Follow-up\n   - To: katie.brown@bluesparrowtech.com\n   - Body: 'Hi Katie,\n   \n   Thanks for attending the client meeting today. Could you please draft a follow-up email summarizing the key points discussed? I''ll review it before sending it to the client.\n   \n   Best,\n   Emma'\n\n3. Re: Client Meeting Follow-up\n   - To: David, Katie\n   - Cc: julie.williams@bluesparrowtech.com\n   - Body: 'Hi Katie,\n   \n   The draft looks good. I''ve made a few minor edits. David and Julie, please review and let me know if you have any further suggestions before we send it to the client.\n   \n   Best,\n   Emma'\n\n4. Meeting Follow-up\n   - To: client@abcindustries.com\n   - Cc: david.smith@bluesparrowtech.com, katie.brown@bluesparrowtech.com\n   - Body: 'Dear Client,\n   \n   Thank you for meeting with us today. Here are the key points we discussed:\n   1. Project timeline and milestones\n   2. Budget and resource allocation\n   3. Next steps and deliverables\n   \n   Please let us know if you have any questions or need further information.\n   \n   Best regards,\n   Emma Johnson\n   Blue Sparrow Tech'\n\n5. Lunch Next Week?\n   - To: sarah.baker@gmail.com\n   - Body: 'Hi Sarah,\n   \n   I hope you''re doing well! Would you be free for lunch next week? It would be great to catch up.\n   \n   Best,\n   Emma'\n\n6. Re: Lunch Next Week?\n   - To: sarah.baker@gmail.com\n   - Body: 'Hi Sarah,\n   \n   Wednesday at 1 PM works perfectly. Let''s meet at our usual spot. Looking forward to it!\n   \n   Best,\n   Emma'\n\n7. Re: Family Reunion\n   - To: james.miller@yahoo.com\n   - Body: 'Hi James,\n   \n   Thanks for the reminder! I''ll be there. Please send me the address and any other details when you get a chance.\n   \n   Looking forward to seeing everyone!\n   \n   Best,\n   Emma'\n\n8. Re: Family Reunion\n   - To: james.miller@yahoo.com\n   - Body: 'Hi James,\n   \n   Thanks for the details! I''ll definitely be there and I''ll bring my famous apple pie for the potluck. I don''t need a place to stay, but I appreciate the offer. If there''s anything else I can help with, please let me know.\n   \n   Looking forward to seeing everyone and catching up!\n   \n   Best,\n   Emma'\n\n9. Re: Hiking Trip\n   - To: mark.davies@hotmail.com\n   - Body: 'Hi Mark,\n   \n   A hiking trip sounds perfect! Count me in. What time should we meet and where?\n   \n   Best,\n   Emma'\n\n10. Tech Issue\n   - To: support@bluesparrowtech.com\n   - Body: 'Hi Support Team,\n   \n   I''m experiencing some issues with my email client. It seems to be running very slowly. Could you please assist?\n   \n   Thanks,\n   Emma'",
